These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
City: rome, new-york, hamburg, hannover
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, daffodil, orchid
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person who growsaconite is the fan of techno##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to hannover##2
3. the person who growsaconite is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
8. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
9. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| City   | new-york | hannover   | rome  | hamburg  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Flower   | orchid | aconite | daffodil | poppy |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

