.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, orange, white, azure
City: berlin, nizza, prague, boston
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
5. the person traveling to boston is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person traveling to boston and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who likes white##1
9. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color         | azure | orange    | white  | fuchsia    |
| City   | berlin      | nizza  | boston  | prague |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

