.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, emerald, pink, grey
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, fanta, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes grey##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who likes black and the person who likes grey##2
9. the person who likes pink is between the person eating lemon and the person drinking sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Color       | emerald   | black   | pink | grey |
| Beverage         | iced-tea   | fanta | water       | sprite    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

