.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, swisher, bongani, dunhill
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
4 different games are played: chess, whist, canasta, domino
 1. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the dunhill-smoker is the fisherman##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
 5. the dunhill-smoker is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is the police-officer##1
 8. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person playing whist##1
10. the mechanic is between the owner of the bird and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Cigar   | dunhill | dannemann  | bongani | swisher       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Game         | chess | whist   | domino   | canasta         |

