.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, sunflower, daffodil
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, september, august
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's birthday is in july##2
10. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Flower           | sunflower | daffodil | tulip    | daisy     |
| Birthday   | july      | september       | august    | january       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

