.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, librarian, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, animation, crime, horror
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, mauve, green, turquise
1. the fan of folk is between the person who likes turquise and the fan of jazz##2
2. the freelancer is between the fan of folk and the person watching horror movies##2
3. the person watching crime movies is between the person who likes mauve and the person watching animation movies##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who likes green##1
7. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | animation      | crime   | zombie   |
| Color         | green   | turquise    | yellow | mauve   |

