 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##2
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the fisherman##1
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
